# NexusCore LLM Routing Rules

## 1. モデル分類（5プロバイダー / 9プロファイル）

Quality Tier:
- gpt-5.5 (OpenAI)
- claude-sonnet-4-6 (Anthropic)
- gemini-3.1-pro (Google)

Lightweight Tier:
- glm-5.1 (Zhipu AI)
- minimax-m2.7 (MiniMax)

## 2. プロファイルマッピング

code_generate:
  - primary: gpt_codex (gpt-5.5)
  - secondary: sonnet_code, glm_default
  - fallback: glm_default

test_generate:
  - primary: gpt_codex (gpt-5.5)
  - secondary: sonnet_code, glm_default
  - fallback: glm_default

code_review:
  - primary: sonnet_review (claude-sonnet-4-6)
  - secondary: gpt_strict, glm_strict
  - fallback: glm_strict

debug:
  - primary: gpt_codex (gpt-5.5)
  - secondary: sonnet_code, glm_default
  - fallback: glm_default

self_heal:
  - primary: gpt_codex (gpt-5.5)
  - secondary: sonnet_code, glm_default
  - fallback: glm_default

architect:
  - primary: sonnet_review (claude-sonnet-4-6)
  - secondary: gpt_strict, glm_strict
  - fallback: glm_strict

plan_generate:
  - primary: sonnet_review (claude-sonnet-4-6)
  - secondary: gpt_strict, gemini_secondary, glm_strict
  - fallback: glm_strict

requirement:
  - primary: sonnet_review (claude-sonnet-4-6)
  - secondary: gpt_strict, glm_strict
  - fallback: glm_strict

general:
  - primary: glm_default (glm-5.1)
  - secondary: minimax_default
  - fallback: glm_default

routing_classify:
  - primary: glm_default (glm-5.1)
  - secondary: minimax_default
  - fallback: glm_default

analytical:
  - primary: minimax_analytical (minimax-m2.7)
  - secondary: gemini_secondary, glm_default
  - fallback: glm_default

## 3. 環境変数
- OPENAI_API_KEY: OpenAI API key
- ANTHROPIC_API_KEY: Anthropic API key
- GEMINI_API_KEY: Google Gemini API key
- GLM_API_KEY: Zhipu AI API key (aliases: ZHIPU_API_KEY, GLM_KEY)
- GLM_API_BASE: GLM base URL (default: https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4)
- GLM_MODEL: Model override (default: glm-5.1)
- MINIMAX_API_KEY: MiniMax API key (alias: MINIMAX_KEY)
- MINIMAX_API_BASE: MiniMax base URL (default: https://api.minimax.chat/v1)
- MINIMAX_MODEL: Model override (default: minimax-m2.7)

## 4. Consensus Algorithm
- signature: normalized hash
- weight: model trust score
- vote: weighted majority
- fallback: primary model output
